If the matter is security related, please disclose it privately via https://kubernetes.io/security/
-->


**What happened**: 
In kubernetes 1.15, Panic happends in kube-apiserver. Subsets[0] is  nil  when endpoints `kubernetes` has no subsets

The Panic happens in here:

https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/release-1.15/pkg/master/reconcilers/mastercount.go#L155


And everything returns to normal when we delete the endpoints `kubernetes` in  etcd 

**What you expected to happen**:
Maybe kube-apiserver should print error,not panic

**How to reproduce it (as minimally and precisely as possible)**:
The host's iowait of ETCD is high
